                              Current    Prior      Change
Revenue growth (%)                                  X.X%
Gross margin (%)              XX.X%      XX.X%      X.X pp
Operating margin (%)          XX.X%      XX.X%      X.X pp
Net margin (%)                XX.X%      XX.X%      X.X pp
OpEx as % of revenue          XX.X%      XX.X%      X.X pp
Effective tax rate (%)        XX.X%      XX.X%      X.X pp
""" ;
                                    oc:codeLanguage "" ;
